[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
3/4 oz [genericingredient Gold Tequila] Sauza Anejo Tequila
3/4 oz [genericingredient Gin] Beefeater Gin
3/4 oz Rum Light
3/4 oz [genericingredient Vodka] Absolut Vodka
3/4 oz [genericingredient Blue Curacao] Hiram Walker Blue Curacao
1 1/2 oz Sweet/Sour Mix
Shake and Strain
Top: Lemon Lime Soda
Garnish: Lemon Slice

